                <h1>The NBA&#039;s black eye</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/741eaae3-35ce-4594-94bd-3f1088c16270.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;Kyrie&#x20;Irving&#x20;has&#x20;been&#x20;among&#x20;the&#x20;list&#x20;of&#x20;former&#x20;Duke&#x20;players&#x20;to&#x20;play&#x20;sporadically&#x20;this&#x20;postseason.&amp;nbsp&#x3B;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>Kyrie Irving has been among the list of former Duke players to play sporadically this postseason.&nbsp;</p>

                                                             <aside class="photo-caption photo-credit d-block pl-1">
                                    <figcaption class="d-block">
                                                                                    Photo by <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/jack-dolgin">Jack Dolgin</a> |
